        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2289686278" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2115435447451342921">I learned quite a bit of new info from this. It&apos;s done in a style of having lots of excerpts from mostly harder to find texts from the period, with the author&apos;s thoughts as well. I really enjoyed this style. I&apos;d like to read follow-ups to this book done in the same style, maybe on the Harlam [sp] renaissance, civil rights, black panthers/black power, and black lives matter. This is an important book for sure and one everyone should read, imo. </span>
  <span id="freeText2115435447451342921" style="display:none">I learned quite a bit of new info from this. It's done in a style of having lots of excerpts from mostly harder to find texts from the period, with the author's thoughts as well. I really enjoyed this style. I'd like to read follow-ups to this book done in the same style, maybe on the Harlam [sp] renaissance, civil rights, black panthers/black power, and black lives matter. This is an important book for sure and one everyone should read, imo. </span>
