<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/15825932-in-the-tall-grass"><img alt="In the Tall Grass" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1346688418l/15825932._SX98_.jpg" />
